{"tid":1566324,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中秋團圓，和勇相聚，大家可唔可以入一入黎聽我講一講？","createTime":"2019-09-13T13:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:19:21.000Z","uid":2377,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5da457e8e43502d3c7f4ff56e1614bbe1cddffdb","tid":1566324,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:49:56.000Z","msg":"今晚中秋節，祝大家中秋快樂先！<br />\n今晚我地和勇相聚<br />\n呢排和理非唱歌都可以被黨媒點名<br />\n證明雖左膠，但有用！<br />\n但呢排我見好多po都屌緊運動左膠化！<br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以於9月13號中秋立誓！<br />\n<br />\n和理非 勇武不互屌<br />\n勇武做錯事，本身就靠我地和理非執返正！<br />\n和理非點左膠化都好，都要記住勇武嘅付出<br />\n有錯大家指出，但係咪屌黎屌去！"},{"pid":"646b14801c9144bed0dcdc93ee4fa6d5df7492a1","tid":1566324,"uid":101537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:51:41.000Z","msg":"和勇不分<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TT5NoYN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTT5NoYN.jpg&h=6894a64b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GvUKrb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvUKrb8.jpg&h=ec6b4d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">12點英領和平請願<br />\n灰磚範圍 英國領土</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2點打後 銅鑼灣自由活動!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【國際戰線】又係我，前英領職員，915見（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565523</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3436206aabfca937ac57ccf40fae3111753c1192","tid":1566324,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:09:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4189307da89b7e18f68a86fbcf84262041b3d13b","tid":1566324,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike